# Placeholder for certificates
# Place the following files in this directory:
#
# SSL Certificates (for Nginx):
#   - fullchain.pem  : SSL certificate chain
#   - privkey.pem    : SSL private key
#
# OpenIddict Certificate (for Authority Server):
#   - certificate.pfx : PKCS12 certificate for token signing
#
# For development, you can generate self-signed certificates:
#   ./scripts/generate-certs.sh your-domain.com
#
# For production, use Let's Encrypt or a trusted CA.
